===================================
Intel Kernel Guard Technology (iKGT, https://01.org/intel-kgt)
Open-sourced in year 2015.
Previously named as TMSL (Trusted Memory Service Layer*) used as anti-malware
core engine of McAfee Deep Defender on Windows PC.

wget https://01.org/sites/default/files/downloads/intel-kgt/ikgtsrc.1.2.1.tar.gz
